sentence: Tuesday's session closes with the NASDAQ Composite Index at 3,129.65.
The total shares traded for the NASDAQ was over 1.81 billion.
Advancers stocks led declining by 1.51 to 1 ratio.
There were 1481 advancers and 982 decliners for the day.
On the NASDAQ Stock Exchange 23 stocks reached a 52 week high and 16 those reaching lows totaled.
The most active, advancers, decliners, unusual volume and most active by dollar volume can be monitored intraday on the Most Active Stocks page.
The NASDAQ 100 index closed up .45% for the day; a total of 12.05 points.
Expeditors International of Washington, Inc. ( EXPD ) had the largest percent change down (-7.33%) while Randgold Resources Limited ( GOLD ) had the largest percent change gain rising 3.52%.
The Dow Jones index closed up .84% for the day; a total of 115.96 points.
UnitedHealth Group Incorporated ( UNH ) had the largest percent change down (-.47%) while Home Depot, Inc. (The) ( HD ) had the largest percent change gain rising 5.69%.
